            <div class="col-lg-6 order-2 order-lg-1 content" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="200">
                <h3>Reading skills for early learners</h3>
                <p class="fst-italic">
                    Our reading worksheets help young learners develop essential reading skills and understanding. We cover phonics, sentence and paragraph building, and engaging stories with accompanying comprehension activities. Our stories are designed to reinforce key comprehension concepts like main idea and sequencing.
