                    <li><i class="bi bi-check-circle"></i> <span>Comprehensive approach: Covers phonics, sentence structure, and comprehension.</span></li>
                    <li><i class="bi bi-check-circle"></i> <span>Strong foundation: Builds on phonics to develop reading skills.</span></li>
                    <li><i class="bi bi-check-circle"></i> <span>Engaging content: Uses children's stories to make learning fun.</span></li>
                    <li><i class="bi bi-check-circle"></i> <span>Skill development: Targets specific comprehension skills.</span></li>
                    <li><i class="bi bi-check-circle"></i> <span>Empowerment: Helps children become confident readers.</span></li>
                     
